msgid "Sometimes renewals will be blocked based on your circulation rules, to override this block you must have your :ref:`AllowRenewalLimitOverride` preference set to 'Allow'. If you allow renewal limit overrides, you will see a checkbox at the bottom left of the circulation summary. Check that box and then choose the items you would like to renew."
